segment.source: This topic for the IT professional describes the Advanced Security Audit policy setting, Audit Other System Events, which determines whether the operating system audits various system events.
segment.target: This topic for the IT professional describes the Advanced Security Audit policy setting, Audit Other System Events, which determines whether the operating system audits various system events.

segment.source: Audit Other System Events contains Windows Firewall Service and Windows Firewall driver start and stop events, failure events for these services and Windows Firewall Service policy processing failures.
segment.target: Audit Other System Events contains Windows Firewall Service and Windows Firewall driver start and stop events, failure events for these services and Windows Firewall Service policy processing failures.

segment.source: Audit Other System Events determines whether the operating system audits various system events.
segment.target: Audit Other System Events determines whether the operating system audits various system events.
